{"id": "last_array_element", "prompt": "Из полученного списка email получи последний.", "expected_mode": "json_with_lua_wrappers", "wf_fixture": {"wf": {"vars": {"emails": ["user1@example.com", "user2@example.com", "user3@example.com"]}}}, "expected_runtime_output": "user3@example.com", "expected_json_key": "lastEmail", "expected_contains": ["wf.vars.emails", "#wf.vars.emails"], "expected_not_contains": ["$.", "jsonpath"]}
{"id": "increment_try_counter", "prompt": "Увеличивай значение переменной try_count_n на каждой итерации", "expected_mode": "json_with_lua_wrappers", "wf_fixture": {"wf": {"vars": {"try_count_n": 3}}}, "expected_runtime_output": 4, "expected_json_key": "try_count_n", "expected_contains": ["wf.vars.try_count_n", "+ 1"], "expected_not_contains": ["$.", "jsonpath"]}
{"id": "cleanup_rest_result_keys", "prompt": "Для полученных данных из предыдущего REST запроса очисти значения переменных ID, ENTITY_ID, CALL", "expected_mode": "json_with_lua_wrappers", "wf_fixture": {"wf": {"vars": {"RESTbody": {"result": [{"ID": 123, "ENTITY_ID": 456, "CALL": "call_1", "EXTRA": "x"}, {"ID": 789, "ENTITY_ID": 101, "CALL": "call_2", "OTHER": "y"}]}}}}, "expected_runtime_output": [{"ID": 123, "ENTITY_ID": 456, "CALL": "call_1"}, {"ID": 789, "ENTITY_ID": 101, "CALL": "call_2"}], "expected_json_key": "result", "expected_contains": ["wf.vars.RESTbody.result", "ID", "ENTITY_ID", "CALL"], "expected_not_contains": ["$.", "jsonpath"]}
{"id": "datum_time_to_iso8601", "prompt": "Преобразуй время из формата 'YYYYMMDD' и 'HHMMSS' в строку в формате ISO 8601 с использованием Lua.", "expected_mode": "json_with_lua_wrappers", "wf_fixture": {"wf": {"vars": {"json": {"IDOC": {"ZCDF_HEAD": {"DATUM": "20231015", "TIME": "153000"}}}}}}, "expected_runtime_output": "2023-10-15T15:30:00.00000Z", "expected_json_key": "time", "expected_contains": ["wf.vars.json.IDOC.ZCDF_HEAD.DATUM", "string.format"], "expected_not_contains": ["$.", "jsonpath"]}
{"id": "iso8601_to_unix", "prompt": "Конвертируй время в переменной recallTime в unix-формат.", "expected_mode": "json_with_lua_wrappers", "wf_fixture": {"wf": {"initVariables": {"recallTime": "2023-10-15T15:30:00+00:00"}}}, "expected_runtime_output": 1697383800, "expected_json_key": "unix_time", "expected_contains": ["wf.initVariables.recallTime", "days_since_epoch"], "expected_not_contains": ["$.", "jsonpath"]}
{"id": "ensure_items_are_arrays", "prompt": "Как преобразовать структуру данных так, чтобы все элементы items в ZCDF_PACKAGES всегда были представлены в виде массивов", "expected_mode": "json_with_lua_wrappers", "wf_fixture": {"wf": {"vars": {"json": {"IDOC": {"ZCDF_HEAD": {"ZCDF_PACKAGES": [{"items": [{"sku": "A"}, {"sku": "B"}]}, {"items": {"sku": "C"}}]}}}}}}, "expected_runtime_output": [{"items": [{"sku": "A"}, {"sku": "B"}]}, {"items": [{"sku": "C"}]}], "expected_json_key": "packages", "expected_contains": ["wf.vars.json.IDOC.ZCDF_HEAD.ZCDF_PACKAGES", "ensureArray", "ipairs"], "expected_not_contains": ["$.", "jsonpath"]}
{"id": "filter_discount_or_markdown", "prompt": "Отфильтруй элементы из массива, чтобы включить только те, у которых есть значения в полях Discount или Markdown.", "expected_mode": "json_with_lua_wrappers", "wf_fixture": {"wf": {"vars": {"parsedCsv": [{"SKU": "A001", "Discount": "10%", "Markdown": ""}, {"SKU": "A002", "Discount": "", "Markdown": "5%"}, {"SKU": "A003", "Discount": null, "Markdown": null}, {"SKU": "A004", "Discount": "", "Markdown": ""}]}}}, "expected_runtime_output": [{"SKU": "A001", "Discount": "10%", "Markdown": ""}, {"SKU": "A002", "Discount": "", "Markdown": "5%"}], "expected_json_key": "result", "expected_contains": ["_utils.array.new", "wf.vars.parsedCsv", "Discount", "Markdown"], "expected_not_contains": ["$.", "jsonpath"]}
{"id": "extend_existing_code_square_number", "prompt": "Добавь переменную с квадратом числа", "expected_mode": "json_with_lua_wrappers", "wf_fixture": {"wf": {"initVariables": {"number": "5", "num": "5"}}}, "expected_runtime_output": {"num": 5, "squared": 25}, "expected_contains": ["squared", "tonumber"], "expected_not_contains": ["$.", "jsonpath"]}
